author: COMSOL
description: In a reciprocating piston engine the connecting rods transfer rotating motion into reciprocating motion. The connecting rods are identified as the critical parts and are analyzed from the fatigue perspective. The fatigue lifetime is predicted using the Basquin high-cycle fatigue criteria.
label: engine_fatigue.mph
